query:
INSERT INTO project_statuses (id, project_id, name, color, sort_order, hidden, created_at)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
            RETURNING
                id              AS "id!: Uuid",
                project_id      AS "project_id!: Uuid",
                name            AS "name!",
                color           AS "color!",
                sort_order      AS "sort_order!",
                hidden          AS "hidden!",
                created_at      AS "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
